than I thought.

00:10.421 --> 00:14.023
And now we are stuck in traffic.

00:14.025 --> 00:15.992
Yeah, bumper to bumper.

00:15.994 --> 00:18.995
Well, tell Ava I'll be there
in an hour, okay?

00:18.997 --> 00:20.413
Okay.

00:21.832 --> 00:23.666
Why didn't you
just tell him the truth?

00:23.668 --> 00:26.235
Because I know
my ex-husband quite well,

00:26.237 --> 00:28.905
and it would really upset him
if he found out

00:28.907 --> 00:31.424
you flew me to San Francisco
in your private jet

00:31.426 --> 00:33.877
just to have fried clams.

00:33.879 --> 00:34.928
Yeah, you're right.

00:34.930 --> 00:36.012
You shouldn't tell him.

00:36.014 --> 00:36.713
Thank you.

00:36.715 --> 00:37.547
I'll tell him.

00:38.600 --> 00:40.016
I just wanted to do
something nice for you

00:40.018 --> 00:41.083
before you went to London.

00:41.085 --> 00:43.052
I'll only be gone a few weeks.

00:43.054 --> 00:45.254
And I...

00:45.256 --> 00:47.106
will miss you.

00:47.108 --> 00:50.059
And I will miss you.

00:51.029 --> 00:52.195
