♪ Men

08:46.150 --> 08:49.395
Hey, can I have 75 bucks
for the new Call of Duty?

08:49.397 --> 08:51.490
$75 for a video game?

08:51.492 --> 08:53.609
Think of it as an investment.

08:56.212 --> 08:57.963
An investment?

08:57.965 --> 09:00.215
Yeah. If I go into the
army after high school,

09:00.217 --> 09:03.168
